body_html:
Thanks gunan.
I am using slackware 14.2 (63-bit).
On checking various issues (including the one that Gunan pointed out), I decided to compile TensorFlow from source. That involved first installing Bazel on my system, but it was successful and now I am able to import tensorflow in python and run various example programs.
